{
  "stem": "24614.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Then there is the Resistance survivors, who were hidden in the woods.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they have a different story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But all of our stories are stories that if the human race doesn't learn from them, they won't learn from anything else.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because there is so much to think about and to wonder.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I myself wonder.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How could I have done this for two and a half years?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even if I tell it in six hours, in 10 hours, in a month, this was two and a half years.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was two and a half years of my life that was taken without any reason, only because I was born Jewish.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think that's part of us survivors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we're telling our story, sometimes we tell it as a matter of fact.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's not as a matter of fact.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We tell it as it is, but it goes fast.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our minutes and hours and days went very, very slow and scary.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have a fifth sense, a sixth sense.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I can hear a bird singing outside, in the middle of the night, because I listened.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My whole two and a half years was listening.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Are they coming for me?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Am I going to live tomorrow?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Are they going to kill me tomorrow?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What's tomorrow going to bring?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Am I going to be able to breathe again free?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I guess, here I am, breathing free, but not as free as I would like to.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I came here to the United States of America in 1946, the United States of America was less anti-Semitic, less prejudiced, less hatred between one and the other.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was less of a lot of things that we should try and get it back like it was.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
